#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:2
msgid "域"
msgstr "Domain"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:3
msgid "域指将网络中多台计算机逻辑上组织到一起，进行集中管理的逻辑环境。域是组织与存储资源的核心管理单元，在域中，至少有一台域控制器，域控制器中保存着整个域的用户帐号和安全数据库。"
msgstr "A domain is a logical environment that organizes multiple computers on a network for centralized management. The domain is the core management unit for organizing and storing resources. A domain has at least one domain controller, which stores the user accounts and security database for the entire domain."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:6
msgid "域结构"
msgstr "Domain Structure"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:9
msgid "域树"
msgstr "Domain Tree"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:10
msgid "域树（Trees）由多个域组成，这些域共享同一表结构和配置，形成一个连续的命名空间（namespace）。"
msgstr "A domain tree consists of multiple domains that share the same schema and configuration and form a contiguous namespace."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:13
msgid "林"
msgstr "Forest"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:14
msgid "林（Forests）是一个复杂的AD实例，由一个或数个域组成，每个域树都有自己唯一的名称空间。"
msgstr "A forest is a complex AD instance composed of one or more domains, and each domain tree has its own unique namespace."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:17
msgid "域控制器"
msgstr "Domain Controller"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:18
msgid ""
"ADDS的目录存储在域控制器(Domain "
"Controller)内，一个域内可以有多台域控制器，每一个域控制器的地位几乎是平等的，有几乎相同的数据库。"
msgstr "The AD DS directory is stored on domain controllers. A domain can have multiple domain controllers, and each domain controller has nearly equal status and an almost identical database."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:20
msgid "在一台域控制器添加一个用户账户后，这个账户会被自动复制到其他域控制器的数据库中。"
msgstr "After a user account is added on one domain controller, the account is automatically replicated to the databases of other domain controllers."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:22
msgid ""
"AD数据库有多主机复制模式（Multi-master Replication Model）和单主机复制模式（Sing-master "
"Replication Model）。"
msgstr "The AD database has a Multi-master Replication Model and a Single-master Replication Model."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:24
msgid "多主机模式可以直接更新任何一台域控制器内的AD对象，并将更新之后的对象复制到其他域控制器，大部分数据都是用多主机模式进行复制。"
msgstr "In multi-master mode, AD objects on any domain controller can be updated directly, and the updated objects are replicated to other domain controllers. Most data is replicated using multi-master mode."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:26
msgid "单主机复制模式是指由一台被称作操作主机（Operations Master）的域控制器负责接收更改数据的请求，并将数据复制到其他的域控制器。"
msgstr "Single-master replication means that one domain controller, called the Operations Master, is responsible for receiving data change requests and replicating the data to other domain controllers."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:29
msgid "信任"
msgstr "Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:30
msgid "两个域之间需要创建信任关系，才可以访问对应域内的资源。"
msgstr "A trust relationship must be created between two domains before resources in the corresponding domain can be accessed."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:33
msgid "域信任类型"
msgstr "Domain Trust Types"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:34
msgid "Active Directory的信任方式可以分为以下几种："
msgstr "Active Directory trust methods can be divided into the following types:"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:36
msgid "Tree-Root Trust"
msgstr "Tree-Root Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:37
msgid "双向具有转移性"
msgstr "Two-way and transitive"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:38
msgid "Parent-Child Trust"
msgstr "Parent-Child Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:39
msgid "具有转移性，双向行人"
msgstr "Transitive and two-way"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:40
msgid "Forest Trust"
msgstr "Forest Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:41
msgid "如果两个林创建了信任关系，则林中所有的域都相互信任"
msgstr "If two forests establish a trust relationship, all domains in the forests trust each other"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:42
msgid "两个林之间的信任关系无法自动扩展到其他林上"
msgstr "A trust relationship between two forests cannot automatically extend to other forests"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:43
msgid "Realm Trust"
msgstr "Realm Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:44
msgid "ADDS域可以和非Windows系统的Kerberos域之间创建信任"
msgstr "An AD DS domain can create a trust with a Kerberos realm on a non-Windows system"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:45
msgid "External Trust"
msgstr "External Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:46
msgid "位于两个林内的域之间可以通过外部信任来创建信任关系"
msgstr "Domains located in two forests can create a trust relationship through an external trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:47
msgid "Shortcut Trust"
msgstr "Shortcut Trust"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:48
msgid "可以缩短验证用户身份的时间"
msgstr "Can shorten the time required to authenticate users"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:51
msgid "OU"
msgstr "OU"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/domain/domain.rst:52
msgid ""
"组织单位（Organization "
"Unit，OU）是一个容器对象，将域中的对象组织成逻辑组，帮助管理员管理。OU包含用户、计算机、工作组、打印机、安全策略以及其他组织单位等。"
msgstr "An Organizational Unit (OU) is a container object that organizes objects in a domain into logical groups to help administrators manage them. An OU can contain users, computers, workgroups, printers, security policies, other OUs, and related objects."
